snippet.title: Crash Team Rumble™ - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Join the heroes and villains of the Crash universe as they face off in an epic team vs. team Wumpa-collecting, island-hopping championship. 

Music by: Frankie Simone
Song: King

A new way to Crash. Coming 2023 #CrashTeamRumble
